summary: My first mod! Just a quick little retexture of the player\'s male Argonian body to have war paint on the body.
descriptionHtml:
Really, it\'s just a simple body paint mod. If you like it and want more colors or a different design, let me know! I sure could use the practice creating textures. 

The white paint with black lines is the default texture.

NOTE: just found out that this mod effects all male Argonians, do not install if you care.

If anyone know a work around let me know.
author: AnArgonianFromOuterSpace
